Finviz + StockTwits Rolling Window Sentiment & Price Correlation Analyzer
Sweeps rolling windows from 5 to 120 minutes (5-min increments) and
produces a single summary graph: avg % gain and unique ticker count per window.

Requirements:
    pip install curl_cffi pandas scipy pytz matplotlib
"""

